             was indicted for <rs id="t17910216-38-off237" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910216-38-off237" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17910216-38-off237" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17910216-38-cd238" type="crimeDate">4th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910216-38-off237 t17910216-38-cd238"></join>, one hundred and twenty pieces of copper money, called halfpence, value 5 s.
            </rs> the monies of 
               
                  <persName id="t17910216-38-victim458" type="victimName">
                     Francis 
                     Cooke
                  <interp inst="t17910216-38-victim458" type="surname" value="Cooke"></interp>
